00:58:03.870 --> 00:58:07.320
as a kind of eight part
serial like series.

00:58:07.320 --> 00:58:14.820
And so we're always looking
for great content and voices

00:58:14.820 --> 00:58:15.597
for podcasts.

00:58:15.597 --> 00:58:16.680
ANN MARIE LIPINSKI: Great.

