00:59:03.840 --> 00:59:10.770
to engage these maybe sort
of more innovative, if not

00:59:10.770 --> 00:59:12.580
unconventional, ways
of communicating?

00:59:12.580 --> 00:59:13.250
So first one.

00:59:13.250 --> 00:59:14.400
ANN MARIE LIPINSKI: Do
you have an example?

00:59:14.400 --> 00:59:15.025
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

