In terms of whether
we, as the Op-Ed page,

01:03:49.960 --> 01:03:54.850
are susceptible to fakery is,
of course, always been a problem

01:03:54.850 --> 01:03:55.930
and always been an issue.

01:03:55.930 --> 01:04:01.110
And the way we deal with it
is we have fact checkers.

01:04:01.110 --> 01:04:04.330
The front line editors and
there's about a dozen of them

01:04:04.330 --> 01:04:07.570
that work with me, part of
their job is to fact check,

01:04:07.570 --> 01:04:09.670
but we also have a
team of fact checkers

01:04:09.670 --> 01:04:11.410
that go through everything.

01:04:11.410 --> 01:04:16.180
And every piece gets at least
some basic fact checking.

01:04:16.180 --> 01:04:19.367
But because we are opinion,
we're allowing for a certain--

01:04:19.367 --> 01:04:21.700
