01:04:21.700 --> 01:04:26.710
to use what they can
say is demonstrably

01:04:26.710 --> 01:04:30.820
reasonably provable fact
to build an argument.

01:04:30.820 --> 01:04:34.580
And if the basic foundation
of that is true and checkable,

01:04:34.580 --> 01:04:39.130
then that passes our first line
test of whether we'll run it

01:04:39.130 --> 01:04:41.150
or not.

